reviews.review_text: best source not a huge fan of summer '73 in general, however this is a good show and this source has several key aud patches, including one for the beautiful Bird Song in set one.

Agreed...best source here Several listings appear for this show.  Most are AUD.  Of the remaining soundboards, there is one that is SBD/AUD matrix, and this re-tracked one.  The matrix is a little too heavy on the AUD side, and I thought maybe it would be cool to get the whole Wall of Sound effect, but it just isn't caputured.  So I conclude this re-tracked SBD version is the best available.
- This one's a nice copy. Very good show.
